StringValues.16: A small stone head. Its glowing red eye appears to be staring at you.
StringValues.14: This item can be hooked on wall hooks. Your Item Enchantment will be tested if you attempt to use an Idol Gem on the head.

EmoteActions.Message: You hear a faint whisper as the power of the head infuses you.
The red glowing eye locks you in its gaze.
A strange faint voice whispers in your ear, "... believe in me."
A voice seems to whisper in your ear, "Another eye and I may bless you with more power."
